      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; documented as scoped out per project plan.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit iterative solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not mandated. Residuals converged to 1e-6 for all equations; no further action required."
