      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; model form selection documented with literature justification.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark performance for confined rotating flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is standard for CPB applications. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification deferred to MRL 3."
