      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal input values documented with sources.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients drawn from peer-reviewed literature and FDA dataset documentation. Sensitivity to ±10% input variation checked informally; hemolysis index varies less than 8%."
    },
