      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental sample provenance documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA GCBP dataset provides five independent test samples across operating range. Sample size adequate for MRL 2 comparison; statistical characterization of inter-sample variability not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative mapping between experimental and simulation inputs documented.",
      "rationale": "Experimental inlet flow rates mapped directly to CFD boundary conditions. Rotational speed applied as moving reference frame angular velocity. Equivalency confirmed qualitatively; formal parameter-space mapping not required at MRL 2."
